,Recommended,220200,23436392,"Posted: 7 June, 2016",all,Solar,"In this game you control every aspect of a space mission, from hiring your crew, to researching technologies, to designing your ship, to launching it into orbit, landing it on another planet (or moon), and safely returning your crew home.WARNING: THIS GAME IS VERY HARDIt is literally rocket science. You will have to learn all about rocket design, staging, and orbital mechanics in order to successfully send your kerbals to the mun and back. You will fail many times, usually resulting in spectacular explosions. But when you finally succeed, and your hours and hours of research, trial and error finally pay off, it is the most satisfying feeling of any video game I have ever played. When your kerbal steps out of the spaceship you designed and piloted, climbs down the ladder, plants the flag, and you look up to admire the beautiful view of kerbin from the mun, you suddenly feel that all those hours of frustration were worth it."
